#: 40304:1215
msgid "Natsume-chan was standing there like a lost child. She looked up and faced me right in the eyes, her gaze full of trust."
msgstr ""

#: 40304:1216
msgid "Then, two contradicting instincts were born inside of me. One wanted to protect her, and the other wanted to make her mine."
msgstr ""

#: 40304:1217
msgid "And there was a way to fulfill both of them at once, and Natsume-chan wanted me to do that as well."
msgstr ""

#: 40304:1218
msgid ""
"{Kazushi}\n"
"\"I understand.\""
msgstr ""

#: 40304:1219
msgid "I nodded, and held her in my arms. I would make her mine to protect her. So that this girl could be loved in this world."
msgstr ""
